(# Viva Questions and Answers \(ASAP Brainwave Classification\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## A\) Basic Project Understanding) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. What is the main objective of this project?) Tj
T*
(- To classify emotional state from EEG signals using DREAMER dataset.) Tj
T*
(- We implemented both:) Tj
T*
(  - 4-class quadrant model \(`Happy`, `Stressed`, `Depressed`, `Calm`\)) Tj
T*
(  - Binary models \(`valence` low/high, `arousal` low/high\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2. Why did you choose EEG-based emotion recognition?) Tj
T*
(- EEG captures brain activity directly, which can be useful for affective computing.) Tj
T*
(- It is a strong ML use-case combining signal processing + deep learning.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3. Which dataset did you use and why?) Tj
T*
(- DREAMER dataset \(`DREAMER.mat`\).) Tj
T*
(- It is a known benchmark in EEG emotion recognition research.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4. What are valence and arousal?) Tj
T*
(- Valence: pleasantness \(negative to positive\).) Tj
T*
(- Arousal: activation level \(calm to excited\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5. How do you map valence-arousal to 4 classes?) Tj
T*
(- High Valence + High Arousal -> Happy) Tj
T*
(- Low Valence + High Arousal -> Stressed) Tj
T*
(- Low Valence + Low Arousal -> Depressed) Tj
T*
(- High Valence + Low Arousal -> Calm) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## B\) Data and Preprocessing) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6. What is the EEG input shape used in your model?) Tj
T*
(- Raw window shape is `\(14 channels, 256 samples\)`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7. Did you do manual preprocessing?) Tj
T*
(- No separate manual step is needed for user.) Tj
T*
(- Pipeline does preprocessing internally during training/inference.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(8. Which preprocessing is used for 4-class path?) Tj
T*
(- Band Power Spectral Density extraction for theta/alpha/beta/gamma.) Tj
T*
(- Baseline removal.) Tj
T*
(- Final feature shape `\(14, 4\)`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(9. Why baseline correction is important?) Tj
T*
(- It reduces subject/session bias and highlights stimulus-driven changes.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(10. How do you avoid data leakage?) Tj
T*
(- Scaler is fit only on training split per fold, then applied to validation data.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## C\) Model Architecture) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(11. Which models are implemented?) Tj
T*
(- `EEGBiLSTMClassifier` for 4-class quadrant prediction.) Tj
ET
endstream
