stream
BT
/F1 11 Tf
50 790 Td
14 TL
(- `EEGNet` for binary valence/arousal prediction.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(12. Why BiLSTM for quadrant model?) Tj
T*
(- It can model sequential dependencies in channel-wise feature sequences.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(13. Why EEGNet for binary tasks?) Tj
T*
(- EEGNet is compact and designed for EEG signals, efficient for low-data settings.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(14. What is confidence score in output?) Tj
T*
(- Probability of predicted class from softmax top value.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(15. How is trial-level prediction done?) Tj
T*
(- By aggregating multiple window predictions:) Tj
T*
(  - majority vote \(with deterministic tie-break\)) Tj
T*
(  - mean probability strategy) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## D\) Training Strategy) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(16. What split strategies are supported?) Tj
T*
(- `cross_trial`, `cross_subject`, `loso`, `group_kfold_subject`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(17. Which split is most reliable for realistic performance?) Tj
T*
(- Subject-independent splits \(`group_kfold_subject` or `loso`\) are more realistic.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(18. Why not trust single-fold accuracy?) Tj
T*
(- Single fold may be lucky/unlucky; multi-fold mean+std is more reliable.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(19. Which metrics are reported?) Tj
T*
(- Accuracy) Tj
T*
(- Balanced Accuracy) Tj
T*
(- Macro F1) Tj
T*
(- \(with mean/std across folds\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(20. Why Balanced Accuracy and Macro F1 are important?) Tj
T*
(- EEG classes can be imbalanced; these metrics are fairer than plain accuracy.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(21. What is early stopping and why used?) Tj
T*
(- Stops training when validation score stops improving.) Tj
T*
(- Prevents overfitting and saves compute time.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(22. What optimization methods are used?) Tj
T*
(- AdamW optimizer) Tj
T*
(- ReduceLROnPlateau scheduler) Tj
T*
(- Optional focal loss, class weights, weighted sampling) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(23. What augmentations are used?) Tj
T*
(- Gaussian noise, channel dropout, and time masking \(configurable\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(24. How is best checkpoint selected?) Tj
T*
(- By composite score:) Tj
T*
(  - `0.7 * balanced_accuracy + 0.3 * macro_f1`) Tj
T*
() Tj
ET
endstream
