(## E\) Engineering and Deployment) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(25. How can a normal user run the project easily?) Tj
T*
(- Through `run.py` commands:) Tj
T*
(  - `python run.py train`) Tj
T*
(  - `python run.py streamlit`) Tj
T*
(  - `python run.py api`) Tj
T*
(  - `python run.py evaluate`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(26. What does Streamlit dashboard provide?) Tj
T*
(- Interactive model selection, payload testing, confidence/probability display.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(27. What API endpoints are available?) Tj
T*
(- `/health`) Tj
T*
(- `/predict/features`) Tj
T*
(- `/predict/window`) Tj
T*
(- `/predict/trial`) Tj
T*
(- `/preprocess/demo`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(28. How did you make project delivery-ready?) Tj
T*
(- Clean folder structure, removed cache/artifact clutter, added documentation.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(29. What files are most important for reviewer?) Tj
T*
(- `run.py`, `streamlit_app.py`, `training/train_eegnet_binary.py`, `inference/api.py`, docs.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(30. How do you ensure reproducibility?) Tj
T*
(- Fixed random seed + controlled split protocol + saved reports/checkpoints.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## F\) Performance and Limitations) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(31. Is this production-ready clinical system?) Tj
T*
(- No. It is a research/demo project for academic use.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(32. Why accuracy may be moderate in EEG emotion tasks?) Tj
T*
(- High inter-subject variability, noisy signals, limited dataset size.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(33. Is 75% guaranteed?) Tj
T*
(- No. It depends on split protocol and training conditions.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(34. What is a realistic way to present results?) Tj
T*
(- Report protocol used, fold-wise mean+std, and limitations honestly.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(35. What are current limitations?) Tj
T*
(- Moderate performance, subject variability, no real EEG device live streaming integration.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## G\) Improvement Questions \(Future Work\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(36. What improvements can be done next?) Tj
T*
(- Better hyperparameter search) Tj
T*
(- Subject adaptation/domain generalization) Tj
T*
(- Advanced time-frequency features) Tj
T*
(- Ensemble or multitask model) Tj
ET
